OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, First Minister Humza Yousaf has ordered
OL,6, a review of Scottish government bank   
OL,7, card spending by civil servants.       
OL,9,FNearly 60,000 transactions, including  
OL,10,Fspending on VIP airport services, worth
OL,11,F#14.2m were made on the procurement    
OL,12,Fcards over a three-year period.        
OL,14,FMr Yousaf said it was "fair to ask the 
OL,15,Fquestions" about the spending and has  
OL,16,Fasked his officials to review          
OL,17,Fprocedures.                            
OL,19,FIt comes as further details of the     
OL,20,Fspending on the cards is revealed.     
